@startuml
actor ClubAdmin
    participant "React Frontend" as React
    participant AuthMiddleware
    participant MerchandiseController
    participant MerchandiseFactory
    participant MerchandiseRepository
    participant MongoDB

    ClubAdmin->React: Login as club admin
    React->AuthMiddleware: POST /api/auth/login {email, password, role:"club_admin"}
    AuthMiddleware-->React: JWT token (role=club_admin)

    ClubAdmin->React: Fill new listing form (type, name, price, sizes)
    React->MerchandiseController: POST /api/merchandise {type, name, price, ...}
    note over MerchandiseController:  AuthMiddleware verifies JWT + role=club_admin
    MerchandiseController->MerchandiseFactory: create(type, data)
    alt type = "tshirt"
        MerchandiseFactory-->MerchandiseController: TshirtProduct
    else type = "hoodie"
        MerchandiseFactory-->MerchandiseController: HoodieProduct
    else type = "cap"
        MerchandiseFactory-->MerchandiseController: CapProduct
    end
    MerchandiseController->MerchandiseRepository: create(product.toDocument())
    MerchandiseRepository->MongoDB: insertOne(merchandise)
    MongoDB-->MerchandiseRepository: Merchandise document
    MerchandiseRepository-->MerchandiseController: Merchandise
    MerchandiseController-->React: 201 Created + listing details
    React-->ClubAdmin: Listing live in catalog

@enduml
